**index.html:**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chess AI</title>
    <style>
        body { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; background-color: #111; margin: 0; }
        canvas { border: 1px solid #333; background-color: #FFFFFF; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <canvas id="chessCanvas" width="1024" height="1024"></canvas>
    <script src="game.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```
