Fragment: append-game-js — Create a function `calculatePseudoMoves(piece, sourceR, sourceC)` that generates pseudo-legal moves (ignoring check/attack rules for now). Implement the Rook movement algorithm (from Q6 pseudocode) and use it to populate `validMoves` when the piece is selected.
